statement: I would rather tackle complex problems than deal with routine tasks.
I would rather collaborate with others than work independently.
I would rather explore how things function in the natural world than focus on abstract concepts.
I would rather create and develop ideas than follow established plans.
I would rather embrace new technologies than avoid them.
I would rather support others in achieving their goals than prioritize my own ambitions.
I would rather interpret data to uncover insights than make decisions based solely on intuition.
I would rather analyze trends and patterns than focus on individual details.
I would rather engage in hands-on activities than spend most of my time in theory.
I would rather coordinate efforts with a team than go solo on projects.
I would rather develop solutions to challenges than stick to traditional methods.
I would rather emphasize well-being and balance than overlook mental health.
